  "title": "Rider (Healthcare/Dispatch/Office Hour)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Dispatch Rider (Healthcare Logistics)</strong></h3><p>(Rider must use own motorcycle)<br /><br /><strong>Location : Western region</strong></p><p><strong>Working Hours: </strong>5.5-day work week</p><h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Collect and deliver medical samples, specimens, and biological materials safely and efficiently</li><li>Ensure proper handling, storage, and temperature control of sensitive materials during transport</li><li>Maintain accurate documentation of collections, deliveries, and any transport incidents</li><li>Plan and optimise delivery routes for efficiency and timeliness</li><li>Perform basic vehicle maintenance to ensure reliability</li><li>Manage urgent and emergency deliveries when required</li><li>Comply strictly with patient confidentiality and PDPA guidelines</li><li>Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Dispatch Rider:</strong> Valid <strong>Class 2B licence</strong> with own motorcycle</li><li><strong>Dispatch Driver (if applicable):</strong> Class 3 licence (holding both Class 2B & Class 3 is an advantage)</li><li>Good verbal and written communication skills</li><li>Basic knowledge of medical terminology and sample handling is preferred</li><li>1–2 years’ experience in courier services or healthcare logistics preferred</li><li>Strong attention to detail and organisational skills</li><li>Able to work independently and as part of a team</li></ul><p>📩<strong>Apply now and help make a difference in healthcare!</strong></p><p>(Only shortlisted candidates will be notified)<br /><br /><strong>EnviroDynamics Solutions Pte</strong> Ltd I EA License No.: 12C6285<br />Lee Pui Shan I Reg. No: R25157211<br /><strong>Email CV to : </strong><a href=\"mailto:jessicalee@envirodynamics.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>jessicalee@envirodynamics.com.sg</strong><br /><br /></a><strong>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to the collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by company relating to this job application</strong></p>",
